{This is a companion hand to Deal 13.

SOUTH has 14 points, the same strength she had in Deal 13. But what a difference. 
This time NORTH's \S shortness complements her hand very well. She bids 4\C 
to show her Control, and after NORTH shows the \DA she 
uses Blackwood to make sure NORTH also has the trump Ace.}

